{"tid":559503,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解恐龍D學名可以咁中二","createTime":"2018-02-13T08:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T09:24:53.000Z","uid":118314,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d23f407c2f8b62ac91ce4759bab8dab43dcc37dc","tid":559503,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"近排打MHW，就去研究D真嘅恐龍資料，發現有D恐龍個學名仲中二過MHW <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>葬火龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.dinosaurpictures.org/citipati_by_himmapaan-d33m6xf_7349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.dinosaurpictures.org%2Fcitipati_by_himmapaan-d33m6xf_7349.jpg&h=d9a9ed4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個名十足十係MHW走出嚟，但個樣係騷鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>通天龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2016/11/17/20161117lw0009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2016%2F11%2F17%2F20161117lw0009.jpg&h=cdea8aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個名霸氣十足，但其實大小同一隻羊差唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天青石龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/29/Nomingia_gobiensis.png/1200px-Nomingia_gobiensis.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F2%2F29%2FNomingia_gobiensis.png%2F1200px-Nomingia_gobiensis.png&h=84e337c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解D鳥型恐龍個名咁撚型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實正確嚟講佢地叫<span style=\"color: blue;\">偷蛋龍科</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暴龍科好多個名都好型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>雄關龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.collecta.biz/collecta_files/products/88706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.collecta.biz%2Fcollecta_files%2Fproducts%2F88706.jpg&h=8cb9be7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>嶼峽龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/Labocania_anomala.jpg/540px-Labocania_anomala.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F7%2F7f%2FLabocania_anomala.jpg%2F540px-Labocania_anomala.jpg&h=79b1625b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蜥腳類唔使多講，如果MHW有蜥腳類可能要打兩三個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">火山齒龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.konglongshijie.com/data/upload/image/201708/bc2c69d8a9ffe1f01499c6f04231e865.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.konglongshijie.com%2Fdata%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F201708%2Fbc2c69d8a9ffe1f01499c6f04231e865.jpg&h=8e2a5186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過呢隻其實好細隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下呢隻係公認最中二 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傷龍，未改名前叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>暴風龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/dinosaurs/images/5/5c/DryptosaurusFeathersColor.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20141125234346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fdinosaurs%2Fimages%2F5%2F5c%2FDryptosaurusFeathersColor.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20141125234346&h=a2c00783&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d8d4c6eef884e15beeca6ab031b52581adb0fbb","tid":559503,"uid":38539,"like":50,"dislike":4,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"史泰龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20140818/photo/bkn-20140818065126882-0818_00862_001_01b.jpg?065154\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20140818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20140818065126882-0818_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F065154&h=30e4295b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6ddb8de9fbda0ef3d134474134fa882729f8040","tid":559503,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d8d4c6eef884e15beeca6ab031b52581adb0fbb","tid":559503,"uid":38539,"like":50,"dislike":4,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"史泰龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20140818/photo/bkn-20140818065126882-0818_00862_001_01b.jpg?065154\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20140818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20140818065126882-0818_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F065154&h=30e4295b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T08:57:47.000Z","msg":"Post 成龍出嚟吖笨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc6b9b7e8f68b11b48b52b2a8dcfb6d49355b34","tid":559503,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d8d4c6eef884e15beeca6ab031b52581adb0fbb","tid":559503,"uid":3853